com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql

Interface ISQLTableHolder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISQLTableHandler<java.lang.Void>

    public interface ISQLTableHolder
extends ISQLTableHandler<java.lang.Void>
    This is an ISQLTableHandler that isn't associated with a specific table but instead manages and controls multiple tables. This is a holder for other tables.
    Author:
    YeetManLord
